1.3.2.name: wordpress/chitika-premium
1.3.2.description:
Reach Your Revenue Potential

Chitika provides its network of over 250,000 publishers with online monetization solutions for both web and mobile sites. Chitika specializes in delivering highly relevant, search-targeted ads drawn from an extensive network of quality advertising partners including; Yahoo! Superpages and yellowbook, boosting user engagement and increasing publisher revenues.

Boost Earnings with Customized Ads

Customize your user experience by choosing the ad unit that best fits your site content and audience. We offer traditional search-target ad units, in addition to our family of Apps including; Chitika Linx (in-text ads) and the newest addition, Chitika Hover.

Don't have a Chitika account? Click here to sign up and get started. Note: Until your Chitika Account is appro
